r id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]γενέσθο̄ ἐν[γ]υάσασθαι \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>.]ΥΣΚΟ̄Ν()ΔΑΜΙΟΣ()ΤΟΥΚΟΒΕΤΟΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>...]ΕΜΟΚΡΙΤΟΣ()ΕΦΙΕΤΟΑΠΕΛΙΝΕΝΓΥΑΣΑΣΘΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>].ΑΔΕΕΦΑΕΙΜΕΙΝΚΑΤΕΛΑΖΕΤΟΤΟΝΛΕΟΝΤΙΝΟ̄ΝΞΕ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΜΥΣΚΟ̄ΝΑ()ΕΝΤΑΙΠΛΑΤΕΙΑΙΘΟ̄ΚΕΟΝΤΑΣ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΑΡΓΥΡΙΟΝΕΧΟ̄ΝHΙΚΕΒΟΟΝΤΙΜΑΝΟΥΚΕΠΡΙΑΤΟ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]..ΠΟΤΕΝΠΕΔΟΚΛΕΤΟΝΜΝΑΣΙΜΑΧΟΥΠΟΤΕ̄ΝΘΕΤΟ\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΓΕΝΕΣΘΟ̄ΕΝ[.]ΥΑΣΑΣΘΑΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030016_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030016_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic030016.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic030016-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Arena 1989 (IGASM I)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: \u003Cspan>Miller: Απέλ̣&lt;λ&gt;ι̣[[ν]]ν\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>[...] Myskon, son of Damis son of Kobetos [...] Anthemokritos bade Apellis offer security [...] said [...] was; he came upon [...] of the Leontines [...] Myskon sitting along the avenue [...] came (not?) having the money, the price of the cattle; he did not buy [...] went to Empedokles, son of Mnasimachos [...] let [...] become (liable?) to act as surety (trans. by Miller).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>[...] Myskon, figlio di Damis figlio di Kobetos [...] Anthemokritos ordinò ad Apelis(?) di agire da garante [...] disse [...] era; si imbatté [...] dei Leontini [...] Myskon seduto lungo il viale [...] venne (non?) avendo il denaro, il prezzo del bestiame; non comprò [...] andò da Empedokles, figlio di Mnasimachos [...] lasciò che [...] diventasse garante.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Miller 1973 fig. p. 37 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002516\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002516\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Brugnone 1980-1981 437-438 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001462\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001462\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1989 77 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Van Effenterre and Ruzé 1995 228-230 no.63 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001022\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001022\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">  Line 1      Line 1    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[198,201,204,207,210,212,215,218,221],{"id":199,"html":200},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> Μ]υσκο̄ν dipunct Δάμιος dipunct τοῦ Κοβέτου \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> Ἀνθ]εμόκριτος dipunct ἐφίετο Ἄπελιν ἐνγυάσασθαι \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]μ̣α δὲ ἔφα εἴμειν κατελάζετο το͂ν Λεοντίνο̄ν ξε-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] Μύσκο̄να dipunct ἐν τᾶι πλατείαι θο̄κέοντας [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] ἀργύριον ἔχο̄ν hῖκε βοο͂ν τιμάν οὐκ ἐπρίατο \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber