"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002516\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002516\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Brugnone 1980-1981 437-438 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001462\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001462\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1989 77 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Van Effenterre and Ruzé 1995 228-230 no.63 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001022\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001022\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":219,"html":220},"handnote","  Line 1      Line 1    ",{"id":222,"html":223},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[225,227,230,231],{"html":226},"Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa",{"id":228,"lang":96,"html":229},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> Μ]υσκο̄ν dipunct Δάμιος dipunct τοῦ Κοβέτου \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> Ἀνθ]εμόκριτος dipunct ἐφίετο Ἄπελιν ἐνγυάσασθαι \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]μ̣α δὲ ἔφα εἴμειν κατελάζετο το͂ν Λεοντίνο̄ν ξε-\u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] Μύσκο̄να dipunct ἐν τᾶι πλατείαι θο̄κέοντας [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] ἀργύριον ἔχο̄ν hῖκε βοο͂ν τιμάν οὐκ ἐπρίατο \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]α̣ι̣ ποτ’ Ἐνπεδοκλε͂ τὸν Μνασιμάχου ποτε̄́νθετο \u003Cbr id=\"al6-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]γενέσθο̄ ἐν[γ]υάσασθαι \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":226},{"id":232,"lang":96,"html":233},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>.]ΥΣΚΟ̄Ν()ΔΑΜΙΟΣ()ΤΟΥΚΟΒΕΤΟΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>...]ΕΜΟΚΡΙΤΟΣ()ΕΦΙΕΤΟΑΠΕΛΙΝΕΝΓΥΑΣΑΣΘΑΙ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>].ΑΔΕΕΦΑΕΙΜΕΙΝΚΑΤΕΛΑΖΕΤΟΤΟΝΛΕΟΝΤΙΝΟ̄ΝΞΕ\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΜΥΣΚΟ̄ΝΑ()ΕΝΤΑΙΠΛΑΤΕΙΑΙΘΟ̄ΚΕΟΝΤΑΣ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΑΡΓΥΡΙΟΝΕΧΟ̄ΝHΙΚΕΒΟΟΝΤΙΜΑΝΟΥΚΕΠΡΙΑΤΟ\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]..ΠΟΤΕΝΠΕΔΟΚΛΕΤΟΝΜΝΑΣΙΜΑΧΟΥΠΟΤΕ̄ΝΘΕΤΟ\u003Cbr id=\"al6-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">6\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΓΕΝΕΣΘΟ̄ΕΝ[.]ΥΑΣΑΣΘΑΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",[235,237],{"image":81,"thumb":236,"title":84},"ISic030016_tiled-thumb.tif",{"image":238,"thumb":239,"title":84},"ISic030016.jpg","ISic030016-thumb.jpg",[],"\u003C?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>\n\u003C?xml-model href=\"https://epidoc.stoa.org/schema/latest/tei-epidoc.rng\" type=\"application/xml\" schematypens=\"http://relaxng.org/ns/structure/1.0\"?>\n\u003